      "writtenOn": "2020-11-09T15:33:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This assumes only back-references are valid (the target fe has already been resolved).  That\u0027s not necessarily the case.  I think for the general case we\u0027ll need a recursive approach to resolve in dependency order.\n\nIt\u0027s ok to start with this though, maybe add a todo.",
